com.badlogic.gdx.ai.btree

Class LeafTask<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.ai.btree.Task<E>
      • com.badlogic.gdx.ai.btree.LeafTask<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of the blackboard object that tasks use to read or modify game state

    @TaskConstraint(minChildren=0,
                maxChildren=0)
public abstract class LeafTask<E>
extends Task<E>
    A LeafTask is a terminal task of a behavior tree, contains action or condition logic, can not have any child.
